Does your child beg to watch Daniel Tiger at times other than 9:30am? Does your child feel angry when you cannot magically make good ole DT appear on the telly? If you answered yes to either of these questions....then this DVD is for you and you sanity. Thanks to this DVD I no longer have to listen to a screaming toddler begging for Daniel and his gang.
